  ('elementary-64311456-moex-00550', 'elementary-64311456', 'elementary-64311456-moex-112-6989845d', 'sub-elementary-64311456-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '社會工作者應該讓社區內不同階層與類別的居民參與社區事務，且應提供居民相互聯繫及參與活動的機 會，以增進對多元文化的尊重。這是屬於下列何種原則？', '["社區自決", "社區關懷", "社區包容", "社區照顧"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:10+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "13927e4759e3", "answer_pdf_sha1": "9f92f5035bc4", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112010", "c": "502", "s": "0303", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作大意", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 15, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "社會行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-64311456-moex-00551', 'elementary-64311456', 'elementary-64311456-moex-112-6989845d', 'sub-elementary-64311456-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何者概念與「案主自決」概念相近？', '["告知後同意", "最小傷害", "相對保密", "絕對保密"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:10+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "13927e4759e3", "answer_pdf_sha1": "9f92f5035bc4", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112010", "c": "502", "s": "0303", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作大意", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 16, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "社會行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-64311456-moex-00552', 'elementary-64311456', 'elementary-64311456-moex-112-6989845d', 'sub-elementary-64311456-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '1869年在英國成立了「慈善組織會社」（Charity Organization Society），在個人接受救濟之前派人瞭解 其是否真正需要接受救助，以避免資源的浪費，當時前往瞭解貧民生活的人員稱為：', '["生活調查員", "友善訪問員", "個案工作員", "家戶審查員"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:10+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "13927e4759e3", "answer_pdf_sha1": "9f92f5035bc4", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112010", "c": "502", "s": "0303", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作大意", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 17, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "社會行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-64311456-moex-00553', 'elementary-64311456', 'elementary-64311456-moex-112-6989845d', 'sub-elementary-64311456-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '在社區發展協會聯繫會報中，四個社區發展協會總幹事描述自己社區特質。大同社區：「本社區一些商 店、公司能提供財源協助辦理活動」；忠義社區：「本社區住戶大都是傳統產業從業人員」；忠孝社區： 「本社區居民以身為社區的一份子為榮」；仁德社區：「本社區是縣內最早設置社區照顧關懷據點的社 區」。上述社區何者最能反映「社區意識」？', '["大同社區", "忠義社區", "忠孝社區", "仁德社區"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:10+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "13927e4759e3", "answer_pdf_sha1": "9f92f5035bc4", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112010", "c": "502", "s": "0303", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作大意", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 18, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "社會行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-64311456-moex-00554', 'elementary-64311456', 'elementary-64311456-moex-112-6989845d', 'sub-elementary-64311456-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '釐清社區相關問題與優先順序，決定要努力改變的目標，並運用具體的工作步驟、方法，協助社區改變， 以解決社區問題。這是下列何種社區工作理論之核心看法？', '["任務中心與任務團體理論", "資源動員與交換理論", "權力與培力理論", "社會計畫與變遷理論"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:10+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "13927e4759e3", "answer_pdf_sha1": "9f92f5035bc4", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112010", "c": "502", "s": "0303", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作大意", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 19, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "社會行政"}'::jsonb, NULL)
